                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-659442660" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="659442660">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/JiaShiLin/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">不是私有化偷窃了俄国人的钱，钱早都被从斯大林到勃烈日涅夫的各任领导人花光了，纸币的购买力仅仅体现在短缺上。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="166461975">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-166461975" class="vote-count">0</span>
